                <ANNOTATION_VALUE>hiyya hāy al-bint kṯīr (t)ḏ̣aḥḥ-ik ʕalē-ah kalimāt yaʕni ǧiddat-i tgūl-hin gabīl kānat tgūl-hin hāḏi tiṭlaʕ tgūli hēk, agūl-ah ēš hāḏ̣a? ʕād ēš baʕdēn tfahim-ni ēš šu maʕana-h</ANNOTATION_VALUE>
