                TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts87" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts88">
                <ANNOTATION_VALUE>iǧa ḥada yāxḏ-u bdūn mā yaṭlub, š-agūl-ū? ma tḥadr-u! yaʕni baʕīd aš-šarr tamūt gabil lā inno, hassa ma tḥadr-u yaʕni ma tnazl-u yaʕni inno lamma yrūḥ ʕa-l-hammām fahimti keyf? yaʕni inta tmūt gabil la trūḥ ʕa-l-hammām</ANNOTATION_VALUE>
